::Kluster::

Kluster frowns. He didn't like this one bit. "Ruthless?"

He shakes his head. That didn't sound like Maximals. Kluster activates his 
comm-link, this had to be figured out.

"Deemos," he says into it, sending the transmission on a Maximal frequency, 
"Return to base at once, I need to speak with you."
